data.description: Welcome to your new home sweet home! This well-maintained, move-in ready gem offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm. Situated in a peaceful neighborhood with no immediate rear neighbors, this single-story abode is ideal for those seeking a starter home or savvy investment opportunity. As you approach, you'll be greeted by a classic brick exterior, manicured landscaping, and a convenient 2-car garage, ensuring both curb appeal and practicality. Step inside to discover a light-filled oasis, featuring high, vaulted ceilings and an inviting open-concept floorplan designed for easy living and entertaining. The spacious living room provides ample space for gatherings and relaxation, seamlessly flowing into the eat-in kitchen. Here, you'll find a chef's dream, complete with ample cabinetry, generous counter space, a sizable pantry, large single-basin stainless-steel sink, and sleek stainless-steel appliances, making meal prep a breeze. Retreat to the large primary suite, boasting a vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet, and private en-suite bathroom with a dual vanity, a deep soaking tub, and separate walk-in shower. Three additional well-sized secondary bedrooms provide versatility for guests, home office, or hobbies. Step outside to the fenced backyard, featuring an extended covered patio, perfect for outdoor dining, relaxation, and enjoying the fresh air in privacy and comfort. Conveniently located less than 5 miles from shopping, dining, and entertainment options, this home offers the best of both worlds: a tranquil retreat away from the hustle and bustle, yet just a short drive from all the amenities you desire. Schedule a showing today!
